question.en:
What does this effectScope pattern accomplish?
```js
const scope = effectScope()
scope.run(() => {
  const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2)
  watch(count, () => console.log('changed'))
})
scope.stop()
```

question.es:
¿Qué logra este patrón effectScope?
```js
const scope = effectScope()
scope.run(() => {
  const doubled = computed(() => count.value * 2)
  watch(count, () => console.log('changed'))
})
scope.stop()
```

